73
00:05:16,609 --> 00:05:18,109
Segera.

74
00:05:19,009 --> 00:05:20,608
Siapa dia?

75
00:05:20,609 --> 00:05:24,608
Putri dari Presiden Oiso yang baru saja kita sebutkan.

76
00:05:24,609 --> 00:05:26,808
Nona Nagami Oiso.

77
00:05:26,809 --> 00:05:28,509
"Nagami Oiso (31), Putri Presiden."

78
00:05:29,609 --> 00:05:33,208
