144
00:08:39,109 --> 00:08:40,708
Dan kau.

145
00:08:40,709 --> 00:08:44,008
Kau menghalangi pencarianku, jadi keluarlah dari kolam.

146
00:08:44,009 --> 00:08:46,508
Tapi, nona,

147
00:08:46,509 --> 00:08:50,108
