148
00:08:50,109 --> 00:08:52,608
Oh, diamlah.

149
00:08:52,609 --> 00:08:54,808
Ini sangat menyebalkan!

150
00:08:54,809 --> 00:08:57,909
Aku akan mencarinya sendiri, jadi semuanya keluarlah!

151
00:09:07,609 --> 00:09:11,909
Aduhai, apa semua gadis kaya itu egois?

152
00:09:13,209 --> 00:09:15,009
Sonoko, kau berbeda, bukan?

153
00:09:16,309 --> 00:09:18,708
Yah, ya.

154
00:09:18,709 --> 00:09:21,809
"Menu makan siang: Curry Stew ala Burgundy" -Terima kasih.

155
00:09:23,309 --> 00:09:25,108
Maaf.

156
00:09:25,109 --> 00:09:27,108
Kita ingin bermain di kolam,

157
00:09:27,109 --> 00:09:28,808
