234
00:13:24,777 --> 00:13:26,276
Begitu.

235
00:13:26,277 --> 00:13:29,076
Jadi mungkin itu sebuah kecelakaan.

236
00:13:29,077 --> 00:13:30,276
Ya.

237
00:13:30,277 --> 00:13:34,876
Mungkin dia mengalami kecelakaan

238
00:13:34,877 --> 00:13:39,776
selagi mengenakan pemberat itu.

239
00:13:39,777 --> 00:13:44,676
Jika dia panik dan kehilangan alat pernafasannya,

240
00:13:44,677 --> 00:13:46,977
